sentences.english: and the mother was very, very disturbed.

sentences.english: Too bad, you best talent is squirting milk from your nose.

sentences.english: The porous nickel was fabricated by using the jet electrodeposition.
sentences.chinese: 採用噴射電沉積方法制備塊體多孔鎳。

sentences.english: Did you spray them with the hose?
sentences.chinese: 你用水龍帶噴他們水了嗎？

sentences.english: The perfume consumer presumably assumes that the volume is resumed.
sentences.chinese: 噴鼻水消費者假定地設想音量已恢復。

sentences.chinese: 適用全部包裝流水線噴刻字碼要求。

sentences.english: Other methods such as jetting and electroosmosis are also available.
sentences.chinese: 使用噴沖和電滲也可以減小下沉阻力。

sentences.english: He points out that there isn't just one answer to the question of what type of printer to buy.
sentences.chinese: 他指出，對於購買何種類型的噴印機，答案不止一個。

sentences.english: Spray carpet cleaner on the stain and scrub it into the carpet with a spoon.
sentences.chinese: 用着色劑把地毯噴乾淨然後用勺把它擦洗到地毯中。

sentences.english: Gadolinium-diethylenetriamine pentaacetic acid (Gd-DTPA)-dimeglumine injection solution was used as the contrast medium.
sentences.chinese: 釓噴酸二甲葡胺注射液被使用爲造影劑。
那就像一條噴着火的龍一樣。

sentences.english: Bits of glass sprayed everywhere when the vase hit the floor and shattered.
sentences.chinese: 那隻花瓶摔到地板碎掉後，玻璃碎片噴得到處都是。

sentences.english: Bring out the cookie cutters, sprinkles, frostings, and cook, then decorate your cookies.
sentences.chinese: 拿出曲奇刀，噴水壺，糖霜就開始裝點你的曲奇吧。

sentences.english: This is an active volcano which spews out lava every year .
sentences.chinese: 這是個每年噴熔岩的活火山。

sentences.english: Take the average temperature in the curing time as curing temperature.
sentences.chinese: 養護溫度取各溼噴樁養護期的平均氣溫。

sentences.english: Brave too long, the city is full of puff of smoke, no place to hide.
sentences.chinese: 勇敢太久，這個城市是充滿煙霧噴，無處藏身。
